        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>Your magic propels you or your ally into forward motion, scattering your enemies when they charge.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Ally (60 ft) - 1 Round - Magical</p><p>You can use this feature as part of the same bonus action when you use @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.rEgvy8ZFH9bI19ym]{Herd's Swiftness}.​</p><ul><li><p>Target ally's walking speed increases by an additional 15 ft.</p></li><li><p>Target ally gains the following:</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Once Per Turn</strong> - 1 Creature (5 ft.)​</p><ul><li><p>While stampeding, if you move at least 20 ft. towards a target and then hit the target with a melee weapon attack:</p></li><li><p>Target takes an extra [[/damage 2d6 bludgeoning]] damage and is pushed up to 10 ft. in a direction of your choice.</p></li></ul>",
